      "solution": {
        "formula": "E[Z] = \\int_0^\\infty 0.04e^{-0.04t}\\left(e^{0.02t}\\right)e^{-0.06t}dt\n= \\int_0^\\infty 0.04e^{-0.08t}dt = \\frac{0.04}{0.08} = \\frac{1}{2}",
