          {
            "step": "This is equivalent to finding m for which \\frac{l_{48+m}}{l_{48}} \u2265 0.5 and \\frac{l_{48+m+1}}{l_{48}} \u2264 0.5."
          },
          {
            "step": "Based on the ILT, we have m = 30 since l_{78} \u2265 4,522,840 and l_{79} \u2264 4,522,840."
          },
          {
            "step": "So: APV = 5000A_{48} + 5000_{30}E_{48}A_{78} = 5000(0.22892) + 5000(0.24193)(0.36044) = 1422.14"
